This TOEFL book is different because it uses an integrated vocabulary learning system called recycling. For each set of ten vocabulary words, you will complete four quizzes:a multiple-choice vocabulary quiza sentence-completion quiza spelling quiza typing quiz This method keeps you integrating and applying new words using six TOEFL skill sets: reading, listening, speaking, writing, spelling and typing. Recycling will help to remember each new word, phrase and idiom more effectively so it can be applied more proficiently on test day.  Bonus materialtyping lessons and tips to improve accuracy and speedlearn how to structure opinion-based and fact-based TOEFL essaysaudio CD to practice listening skills 
